# /oss-flow — Open Source Hub Workflow

**Trigger:** Run ONLY when the user message is exactly `/oss-flow` or starts with `/oss-flow`. Otherwise ignore this rule.

Follow `~/.cursor/commands/oss-flow.md` in full.

**Identity (STRICT):** Run `gh api user -q .login` — must be `AsifAd`. Any other account → STOP, print error, tell user to `gh auth switch`. Re-check before every commit/push/PR.

**Testing is mandatory before every push — miss nothing:** upstream tests, full E2E (96 tests), JSON sanity, manual smoke, CI green after push.

**Finish:** identity check → commit → push `main` → site live ~20s
